{{Top}}
"'''Life tree'''" was the [[Galactic Basic Standard]] equivalent of an [[Ewokese]] phrase referring to the giant [[conifer]]s that grew on [[Endor]]. While "life tree" was the generic term, there existed three dozen Ewokese words for this type of [[tree]].<ref name="CL 2016">[[Star Wars: Complete Locations (2016)|''Star Wars: Complete Locations'']]</ref>

